Deng '''taba''' ('''fats''' king Ingles) metung lang maleparan a grupu da reng compound a keraklan malalaso (''solube'') kareng paglasong organic (organic solvents) at keraklan e malalaso king danum.   [[w:Chemistry|Basi king sangkap dang kemikal]], bibilugan da lang [[ester|triesters]] ning [[glycerol]] ampong [[fatty acid]] deng taba. Maliari lang likidu o solidu king karaniwang [[temperatura]] (room temperature) deng taba, dependi king karelang pamibalangkas (structure) ampong sangkap (composition). Lipat ning gagamitan da la reng katayang "[[laru]]" (''oils''), "taba" (''fats''), ampong "[[lipid]]" ba lang tunggen deng taba, maralas, gagamitan de ing "laru" kareng tabang likidu king karaniwang temperatura, kabang "taba" no man deng tabang solidu king karaniwang temperatura. Ita namang "lipid," magagamit ya kareng likidu o solidung taba. Gagamitan de ing katayang "laru" king sanumang sangkap (''substance'') a e misasamut king danum at kasalat laru, antimo ing [[petroleu]] (o krudu) ampo ing heating oil (larung pamaling bale), nanuman ing kayang pamibalangkas a kemikal (chemical structure).<ref>{{cite book
